Name: JumpCubox
About the game: JumpCubox is a physics-based 2.5D platformer. Roll and jump your cube through harsh traps in order to reach the goal. You have 30 levels to complete, collecting coins as you go! There are 3 coins in each level. ・Level clear: Reach the goal safely! ・Coins: Find the coins and get them! ・Time Attack: Try to complete each level within the time set for it! You can also wall jump, climb up hills, touch switches to open doors, and clear various other gimmicks!
